          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>
            OAuth 2.0 provides secure delegated access, allowing applications to access resources on behalf of users without exposing credentials. 
            Our OAuth implementation supports industry-standard flows for secure authentication and authorization.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="mt-4">Key Features</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Support for Client Credentials flow for machine-to-machine authentication</li>
            <li>Dynamic Client Registration (DCR) for automated client management</li>
            <li>JWT access tokens with customizable claims</li>
            <li>Token introspection and revocation capabilities</li>
            <li>Secure token storage and rotation</li>
          </ul>

